    <item>
      <title>经历艰难的 100 天后，斯塔默回归竞选基本工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/starmer-returns-to-campaign-basics-after-a-rough-first-100-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一上午，基尔·斯塔默在唐宁街召集他的新高层团队时，几乎没有迹象表明几个小时前迫使他的新政府尴尬地重新调整的戏剧性事件已经发生。低调的首相做了介绍，并告诉助手们“继续努力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/starmer-returns-to-campaign-basics-after-a-rough-first-100-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛保守党因不平等问题面临失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/conservatives-heading-for-defeat-in-lithuania-over-inequality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛人很可能会在周日的选举中推翻执政的保守派，因为这个波罗的海国家——北约对俄罗斯乌克兰战争最直言不讳的批评者之一——的选民希望更加注重缩小经济差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/conservatives-heading-for-defeat-in-lithuania-over-inequality</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国公布振兴经济、结束房地产市场低迷计划的关键要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/key-takeaways-as-china-outlines-plans-to-revive-economy-end-housing-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场迫切希望了解中国为恢复经济增长和结束房地产市场低迷所做出的努力，以下是中国财政部长兰福安及其同事今天通报的五个要点。彭博终端读者可以点击此处查看完整记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/key-takeaways-as-china-outlines-plans-to-revive-economy-end-housing-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 04:48:34 GMT</pubDate>
