      <title>墨西哥锡那罗亚州毒品暴力事件导致 200 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/mexico-narcos-violence-between-chapo-mayo-factions-leaves-200-dead-in-sinaloa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地调查机构报道，过去一个月，锡那罗亚贩毒集团内部各派系之间的战斗导致墨西哥州暴力事件激增，已造成 200 多人死亡，234 人失踪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/mexico-narcos-violence-between-chapo-mayo-factions-leaves-200-dead-in-sinaloa</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 00:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
